Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是失憶癥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:07.35,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(665,660)}Amnesia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之八 追憶少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失憶癥..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.38,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,660)}Amnesia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子的那個天真爛漫的性格就是這麼創造出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造人格？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候如果做壞事會被大人教訓對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被教訓時害怕的記憶變成了心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即便長大了也不會想去幹壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果沒有那段記憶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算之後從認識上知道那是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是從感覺上並不能真的認同那是壞事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的人格可以說是根據過去的記憶所塑造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據過去的經驗 行動和生活方式相應改變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果人們真能把那些讓人哭鬧的負面記憶全部舍棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定就會變成她那樣輕鬆安逸的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在連關於新谷的記憶都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子說不定已經不是你所認識的夕子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼夕子人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟我說還是不要再見面比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是你就厚著臉皮退讓了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你打算怎麼辦 新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是以調查夕子學姐的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回夕子學姐的記憶為目的而開始的靈異調查部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算知道了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐也自發選擇遺忘那段記憶的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個部繼續下去也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都沒有在問你這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所問的是 新谷..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想和夕子言歸於好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！妳幹什麼呀 霧江同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真正的笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要真的這麼想 不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正活生生的人和死去的幽靈..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也把夕子忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 如果無論如何都忘不了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來成為夕子的代替吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把頭髮留長了一定很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑啦開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼笑得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明說過我也是個女生啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木啊 說你充滿行動力又可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凈誇你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是那樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不否認嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她眼中的你一定是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說這雖然算不上什麼正當理由..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可正是在這種時候 做個那樣的自己不也挺好的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我要敢於付諸行動..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是夕子學姐已經不認識我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說我和她將是初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這樣的她我該說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再來見我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子說不定已經不是你所認識的夕子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事也太..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去叫人幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我只是稍微摔了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還沒有習慣拐杖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心得心臟都要停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為靈異調查部的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我們很重要的成員 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來撐著你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 這個就..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣 其實很有力氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是要回教室嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能幫上新谷同學的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在不勝光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 身體再往我這邊靠一點沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是病人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從旁照顧是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我受傷的是腳啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的身體是很纖細的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我們還是謹慎起見..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去部室露面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳有點不方便去..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舊校舍的地板不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再摔一跤就不好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把腳治好 然後早日歸部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下一口是煎蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手滑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拐杖換掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過一想到不再需要我幫忙就..有點遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你馬上就能歸部了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？歸部是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是回到靈異調查部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小此木同學真的很擅長料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼球從那種地方飛出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別來礙事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我來這裡有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷真的覺得這樣就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣是指什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛 我會很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想你們真的結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話我也就沒什麼好說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣..有話說清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點不像霧江同學的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底幹了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾是那麼的憧憬啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了 霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是擔心我的時候吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧江同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼..到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴鐺？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 很沒禮貌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買點飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那就隨妳挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈異調查部日記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉強哦 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐也真是的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多久沒有喊出“夕子學姐”這個名字了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成..夕子學姐在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的風有點大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才差點在那邊摔跤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西川和河東同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難不成就是那個新谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸~蠻可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是桃繪喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妳們在說什麼呀 真是的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明整天都在說新谷同學好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡我們作為朋友必須品鑒一下才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學充滿行動力又可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一直覺得很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很憧憬那樣的你..對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點都不帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在靈異調查部裏的時候 新谷同學很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種為了某件事認真地努力著..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了某個人拼命加油的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得就是這種地方很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了某個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很努力？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..新谷同學有喜歡的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡..的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡..的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然..說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隱隱約約察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然察覺到了..還是稍微..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試著努力過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 小此木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個地方我非去不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算去部室也..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要見夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..不是已經看不見夕子了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！如果我的感受是真的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能再次看到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子已經忘掉了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你做什麼她都想不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎麼可能會把因痛苦而放手的東西重新想起來呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果記憶是夕子學姐的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我不想讓她繼續缺失下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我也不想忘了夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子..學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然夕子學姐可能不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃便當 一起散步 一起午睡 一起聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起解開各種怪談之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路之後在舊校舍的大鏡子之前..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邂逅了夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了地下的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創辦了靈異調查部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是..誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和夕子學姐一起生活過的新谷貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得在靈異調查部的時光很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之所以要調查夕子學姐的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我想要了解夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真正想了解的..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夕子學姐妳本人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡..夕子學姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 露出那種表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回憶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕一點點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣都不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕現在也好 請把我記住吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對..對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..那 那個..誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又一次觸摸到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你第一次觸摸到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐 妳的記憶..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都記得哦 貞一的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是為什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧 我胸膛中的感情是如此的高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞一 我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜歡夕子學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞一..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不..那個..這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同學喜歡的是舊校舍的幽靈夕子學姐呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對於那種有名的怪談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的無名小花怎麼贏得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是啦 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的不是..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜歡夕子學姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞一 最喜歡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果夕子把對新谷的記憶和感情分離出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那段記憶至今為止都到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴鐺的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影..夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候..是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是..誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把離失之時間..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把遺忘之記憶..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來..再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福如此痛楚..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之九 怨念少女
